  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"async\">async</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\">@angular/core</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a> } from <a href=\"api/core/testing\">'@angular/core/testing'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L12-L60\">core/testing/src/async.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\nfunction <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(fn: Function): (done: any) =&gt; any;\n</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"co37zyup43k1bj6do68hwz471\">将测试函数包装在异步测试区域中。当此区域内的所有异步调用完成时，测试将自动完成。可用于包装 \n<a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\"><code>inject</code></a> 调用。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7ox89uffraofl00vyy63uanon\">范例：</p>\n<code-example>\nit('...', <a href=\"api/core/testing/async\" class=\"code-anchor\">async</a>(<a href=\"api/core/testing/inject\" class=\"code-anchor\">inject</a>([AClass], (object) =&gt; {\n  object.doSomething.then(() =&gt; {\n    expect(...);\n  })\n});\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common/AsyncPipe\n - api/common/NgIf\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/fakeAsync\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - api/core/testing/tick\n - api/http/testing/MockBackend\n - guide/http\n - guide/pipes\n - guide/reactive-forms\n - guide/router\n - guide/rx-library\n - guide/testing\n - guide/upgrade\n - tutorial/toh-pt6\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/core/testing\n - api/core/testing/async#async\n - api/core/testing/async#description\n - api/core/testing/inject\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/core/testing/src/async.ts#L12-L60\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/core\n-->"
